---
title: "{{ i18n.syllabus.title }}"
subtitle: "{{ course.title }}{% if course.subtitle is defined and course.subtitle %}: {{ course.subtitle }}{% endif %}"
author: "{{ course.instructors | map(attribute='name') | join(', ') }}"
organization: "{{ course.organization.institution }}"
institute: "{{ course.organization.institute }}"
email: "{{ course.instructors | selectattr('email', 'defined') | map(attribute='email') | join(', ') }}"
course: "{{ course.title }}"
term: "{{ course.semester }}"
lang: "{{ course.language | default('en') }}"
format:
  html: default
  pdf:
    documentclass: article
    papersize: a4
    toc: false
    include-in-header: ../assets/latex/_handout-packages.tex
    template-partials:
      - ../assets/latex/before-body.tex
---

## {{ i18n.syllabus.course_information }}

| | |
|---|---|
| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.course }}** | {{ course.title }} |
{% if course.subtitle is defined and course.subtitle %}| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.subtitle }}** | {{ course.subtitle }} |
{% endif %}| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.semester }}** | {{ course.semester }} |
| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.ects }}** | {{ course.ects }} |
| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.language }}** | {{ course.language | upper }} |
| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.institution }}** | {{ course.organization.institution }} |
| **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.department }}** | {{ course.organization.department }} |

## {{ i18n.syllabus.instructors }}

{% for inst in course.instructors %}
- **{{ inst.name }}**{% if inst.role is defined %} ({{ inst.role }}){% endif %}{% if inst.email is defined %} — {{ inst.email }}{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

## {{ i18n.syllabus.schedule }}

- **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.start }}:** {{ course.schedule.start_date }}
- **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.end }}:** {{ course.schedule.end_date }}
- **{{ i18n.syllabus.labels.weekly_day }}:** {{ course.schedule.weekly_day }}

## {{ i18n.syllabus.modules }}

| {{ i18n.syllabus.table_headers.num }} | {{ i18n.syllabus.table_headers.date }} | {{ i18n.syllabus.table_headers.title }} | 
|---|------|-------|
{% for module in modules %}| {{ loop.index }} | {{ module.date.strftime('%d.%m.%Y') if module.date is defined else i18n.syllabus.tbd }} | [{{ module.subtitle }}](modules/{{ module.id }}.qmd) |
{% endfor %}

